snippet.title: Best VGM 689 - Conker's Bad Fur Day - Sloprano (The Great Mighty Poo)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 462 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aWh7crjCWlM

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo 64
Conker's Bad Fur Day (2001)
Sloprano (The Great Mighty Poo)
Robin Beanland
